messages.content: I apologize, but I do not have access to real-time information about the current date. The date depends on when you are asking this question. To find out today's date, you can look at a calendar, check your device's clock, or ask someone near you.
What day of the week would it be if today were 21 September 2025?
If 21 September 2025 were today, it would be a Sunday.
Wow how did you figure that out?

I used my built-in calendar calculation capabilities. Computers and AI systems can quickly calculate the day of the week for any given date by using standard calendar algorithms. These algorithms take into account the rules of the Gregorian calendar, including leap years and other calendar adjustments. 

For most dates, there are mathematical formulas or lookup tables that can quickly determine the day of the week. In this case, I was able to instantly calculate that September 21, 2025 falls on a Sunday.
What day of the week was 29 October 1929?

29 October 1929 was a Tuesday. This was the day of the stock market crash known as "Black Tuesday," which marked the beginning of the Great Depression in the United States. The stock market experienced a devastating collapse on this day, with the Dow Jones Industrial Average dropping significantly and setting the stage for major economic hardship in the following years.
